2001-3245 (La. 10/14/02)

STATE ex rel. Charles MADUELL v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 2001-KH-3245. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Maduell, Charles; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. J, No. 247-942.

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.8; State ex rel. Glover v. State, 93-2330 (La.9/5/95), 660 So.2d 1189.
